parameters: \>\tr<Red Signal> Doctor, are you alright? I've come to help.

\>\tr<Blue Signal> I can't believe there's such a space in the detention
center... What could it possibly be for...?

\tl<Gundead Executive> Hey, I've been waiting. It seems like it took you quite
a while.

\>\tr<Yellow Signal> How dare you do as you please in our base! Be
prepared!
\>\tr<Blue Signal> Is this... the work of only you...?

\tl<Gundead Executive> Hahaha!! That's right. My ability is hypnotic induction.
I've been waiting for a long time, gathering the pent-up frustrations
of humans and causing internal collapse.

\tl<Gundead Executive> This base is truly magnificent. From now on, let's make
effective use of it as a facility for Gandead. Staff members, please
continue to work hard.

\>\tr<Red Signal> Don't be ridiculous!! There isn't a single person in
this base who would obediently work for Gandead.

\tl<Gundead Executive> Is that so? Do you think I was able to move this far
without any collaborators on the inside?

\tl<Gundead Executive> Well, it's already irrelevant to you. Let's have the
disobedient staff work under stronger brainwashing. They have become
the foundation for the reorganization of the new organization.

\>\tr<Yellow Signal> How annoying! I'll just send you flying and solve
everything myself!

\>\tr<Red Signal> Y-Yes!! We have authorization for immediate use of force
and execution by explosive killing based on the Gandead
Countermeasures Act!!
\>\tr<Red Signal> You despicable Gandead executive!! Prepare yourself!

\tl<Gundead Executive> Hmm, I suppose there's no helping it. Let me inflict a
little pain on you first, and then I'll make you listen carefully.
\>\tl<Gandead Executive> \{\{ What a waste of a strategy~!!
There is no chance of winning in the current state.
There is no chance of winning in the current state.
I obtained the mental stabilizer medication!

\tr<Red Signal> Damn... I can't afford to be caught in a situation like
this... I need to hurry... and rendezvous... I have to save the doctor
too.

\c[3] Let's go rescue Blue and Yellow. We can confirm the state of
their humiliation through communication with Blue. If we keep losing,
the situation will only worsen.

\c[3] Furthermore, the current situation of the doctor can be
confirmed through communication with Yellow.

Um, what on earth is happening here? Can you please release me
already?
\tr<Red Signal> Senpai!! Are you okay? I'll help you right away!!

All members of Signal Force have been rescued!! Once we regroup, we
will move on to counterattack!!
Do you want to fully recover the team?
I got a supply of energy drinks until morning!
I got a supply of energy drinks until morning!
